OL,6,FPolice are warning parents about a
OL,7,FSnapchat group on the island which
OL,8,Fthey say contains 'harmful content'
OL,9,Fand is being viewed by children 'as
OL,10,Fyoung as seven'.
OL,12,FMore than 50 local children are
OL,13,Fthought to be part of the group.
