OL,3,CWarning over Guernsey Snapchat group
OL,4,Cexposing children to 'harmful' content
OL,6,FOfficer Laura Simpson said "Snapchat
OL,7,Fis not suitable for children at all.
OL,8,FThe age restriction of 13+ clearly
OL,9,Fisn't deterring families from allowing
OL,10,Ftheir children into this environment,
OL,11,Fand that is putting children at
OL,12,Fserious risk of sexual exploitation.
OL,14,FShe continued "although SnapChat has
OL,15,Fsome parental controls, they are never
OL,16,Fgoing to be as effective as honest,
OL,17,Fopen conversations with your families
OL,18,Fabout what to do if you receive
OL,19,Funwanted contact."
